Module hu.unipannon.virt.plot
Package hu.unipannon.virt.plot.fluent

Class FrameStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.fluent.FrameStyle
  • public class FrameStyle
extends java.lang.Object
    Fluent interface responsible for setting attributes of the frame that are not related to the plot actually displayed. Holds different setting data in Setting classes
    Author:
    Tóth Bálint
